WinUSB v3.5.0.1WinUSB v3.5.0.1 &#xDF; MultiBoot Usb Tool - 2017

WinUSB is a small utility that does not require installation, which will allow you to create a bootable USB disk with Windows without formatting and loss of important files.&#xA0;In modern times, creating a bootable USB disk for installing Windows is not a big problem, because a lot of different software on this topic was released.&#xA0;However, almost all of them require formatting the drive itself before performing other operations, which is not entirely convenient.

This development will create a multi-boot disk without losing important data from the drive itself.&#xA0;You can select from the list the USB drive you need, then select an ISO image or DVD, then you can format it if necessary, or you can skip this step.

No additional settings are required when working with this program, you just need to perform a few simple steps that will lead you to the desired goal.&#xA0;After starting it is necessary to choose which removable device you want to use, then you need to select the installation DVD disc with Windows 7 and higher or specify the ISO image on the HDD if there is one.&#xA0;Then you can choose which file system you want to create.&#xA0;The process of formatting is optional, but be careful and make sure immediately that the required location is available, otherwise there may be problems.

Summarizing all of the above, we can conclude that we have a really easy-to-use program for creating a boot disk, which differs from the majority only in that it will not be necessary to format the disk, but if you look globally, everything is like everyone else, somewhere even inferior to its competitors, so make your own conclusions, gentlemen.

